column3: You be good to Byakko! He's like a big surly brother to us all!
Well I'll be, he didn't kill you! Shame─I had a bet with the others. Nothing personal, mind. No need to chase anyone into the sea or anything silly like that! Eh!?
By the kami, it's been too long since I've had quality tako-yaki!
Oh, bugger... The urchin girl wanted me to give it to Soroban...
